Package: risoma
Title: Comprehensive Analysis of microRNA Isoforms (isomiRs) with Enhanced 
        Detection Sensitivity and Parameter Flexibility
Version: 0.1.0
Description: risoma integrates modules for miRBase database loading, isomiR 
             identification, expression quantification, differential analysis, 
             and interactive visualization. The tool innovatively introduces a 
             strategy of independently controlling insertion-deletion (InDel) 
             and single nucleotide polymorphism (SNP) thresholds across distinct 
             regions (5\' end, central region, 3\' end) through an improved 
             "seed-and-extension" algorithm, significantly enhancing the 
             detection sensitivity for complex variants. 
